1 new good preset changed my whole business, here is how: I also thought using those popular moody presets that all the wedding photographers are using will be the key to success. But guess what? My clients in the Netherlands had a different idea!

The weather here is mostly gray & depressing. But, I was capturing moments at happy festivals and weddings, and my clients wanted their photos to be full with vibrant colors and pure joy! They didn‚Äôt want moody shots. they wanted their memories to come alive!

So I went looking for those vibrant presets but all the beautiful presets I found were making the green look gray which I can‚Äôt have because the Netherlands is completely green! Thats where I understood I needed to create my own Lightroom presets to give my photos that wow factor and have my clients happy, I wanted them to be full of life.

Today, I‚Äôm thrilled to share my creation with you. The GOLD presets are the secret to capturing the true essence of your memories, ensuring each shot is filled with breathtaking colors and pure joy.

A never-ending cycle of taking 5000 photos during a shoot and then spending hours selecting them. 

Here is what helps me select faster:
1. Trust your intuition - if a photo catches your eye, it‚Äôs probably worth keeping. 
2. Choose with emotion - which photos do you feel most connected to? Which ones capture the essence of the moment?
3. Choose the photos you can see them using as a profile photo the most
